Startpage by Paul Bakker

Requirements: Apache with PHP and MySQL.

Installation:
In order to install startpage you have to edit config.php so it contains the correct
information for the MySQL database. After this you can run startpage-create.php to
create a basic installation of the tables required.
WARNING: It is wise to remove startpage-create.php from this folder after that or remove
its read rights, as this script will clear your startpage database if run another time!!!

Configuration:
You can further configure the look from the page from config.php or the stylesheet used.

Features:
* Group links in categories.
* Count of link clicks for dynamic ordering of links and categories.

For questions and suggestions, you can mail me at p.j.bakker@brainspark.nl
